column16: Christian Colon grounds out, third baseman Nick Castellanos to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
Whit Merrifield walks.   Cheslor Cuthbert to 2nd.

Cheslor Cuthbert grounds into a force out, third baseman Nick Castellanos to second baseman Ian Kinsler.   Kendrys Morales scores.    Paulo Orlando to 3rd.    Jarrod Dyson out at 2nd.    Cheslor Cuthbert to 1st.
Jarrod Dyson walks.   Paulo Orlando to 2nd.
